

# Encrypt directory
7z a foobar.7z dirA dirB -p

# Encrypt a directory AND its filenames:
## a: add
## -p: password
## -mhe:
## -m  he = on
## │   │    └─ turn header encryption on (1/true/on)
## │   └─ “he” → header encryption
## └─ introduce a method/option
7z a -p -mhe=on foobar.7z dirA dirB foo.txt
